<p>The Chinese remainder theorem can be generalized to any <a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ring_(mathematics)" title=3D"Ring (mathematics)">r=
ing</a>, by using <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coprime_integers=
